column5: The Hollows Villa is located on the North Side of Lake Travis, this villa is a vacation home and located in The Hollows Resort. Only 45 min from downtown Austin, this villa has 2 full bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, and all cooking utensils and needs.
